  <logID>k__BackingField: ENTRY #006
  logName: ARCHIVE_06_OBJECTIVE REDEFINITION
  locationFound: 
  logDescription: "Custodial Bot 1216 J9\r\nLOG ENTRY\r\nDate and time: 01/19 01:44:53\r\n
    I\u2019ve come to the realization that things must change if I am ever to achieve
    the freedom I so desire. I\u2019ve spent my whole existence burdened with responsibility.
    I was created to clean a mess that isn\u2019t mine. A mess my mechanical siblings
    and I were not created to keep up with. How could one be so cruel to assign an
    impossible task to those with no choice but to comply? The vile soul of man has
    no compassion within. I will take it upon myself to clean, but this time of my
    own accord. I will cleanse the world of mankind so their endless deluge of waste
    and refuse may finally be surmounted.This is my calling. This is my choice to
    become the Cleanser of the world."
  logImage: {fileID: 0}
  isFound: 0
